-- Sasol Names Alan Cameron as Head of Its Oil Unit, Replacing Maurice Radebe
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 2010-09-29T08:43:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-29/sasol-names-alan-cameron-as-head-of-its-oil-unit-replacing-maurice-radebe.html
Sasol Ltd. said it’s appointed Alan
Cameron, the current managing director of Sasol Solvents, as the
new head of its Sasol Oil unit, replacing Maurice Radebe, who’s
been appointed to the company’s executive committee.  Sasol commented in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  